data.description: Welcome to your new home in charming San Tan Valley, Arizona, a place perfectly situated to experience the benefits of a nearby big city, with the convenience, comfort, and community of small town living!  The friendly neighborhood of Superstition Views is the perfect place for you to live, with a private resident's only swimming pool, lots of green belts for neighborhood gatherings.  You'll be charmed by the atmosphere of this beautifully updated home.   The heart of this home is the kitchen with lovely modern white quartz waterfall edge countertop and white cabinets, stainless appliances, wood look luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, so easy care, and durable. The living/dining area create an open, cozy relaxing entertaining space off the wonderful kitchen. You will love the updated bathrooms, with gorgeous tile surround, white quartz vanity tops, fabulous HUGE shower in the primary bath, creating a spa like atmosphere in the primary suite, and so much more!  The back yard has a great covered patio, with artificial turf, creating the easy care relaxing area to spend time enjoying the climate and take time to go view the gorgeous Superstition Mountains the community is named after.  The conveniently located Resident's only pool, and community facilities directly behind the back yard across greenbelt.  Come to lovely San Tan Valley nestled in the San Tan Mountains, the perfect place to call home!
